title: Spain 15 Year Bond Yield
description: Spain 15Y was 3.63 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Spain 15 Year Bond Yield reached an all time high of 12.44 in March of 1995. This page includes a chart with historical data for Spain 15 Year Bond Yield.
author: Tesoro Público
